Subject to the terms and conditions of this License, contributors grant you a free, perpetual, non-exclusive, no-charge, royalty-free, irrevocable copyright license to use, copy, modify, merge, publish, distribute, sublicense, and/or sell copies of the Bitpulse software and to permit persons to whom the Software is furnished to do so.

2. Relationship with Bitcoin
Bitpulse is a fork of Bitcoin, aiming to introduce a supplementary supply mechanism to the existing Bitcoin ecosystem. This project inherits the core principles and functionality of Bitcoin but seeks to explore and implement changes that address the limitations of Bitcoin's capped supply.

